# Assets Loans And Receivables Term Interest Only Approved Amount

## identifier
de7654

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of interest only term loans held by the reporting party and which were approved during the relevant period, irrespective of whether the funds have been advanced to the borrower.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.LoansAndReceivables.TermInterestOnlyApproved.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo5.02.05
- period=duration
